HEADWORD: Frithstool
<hw>Frith`stool"</hw> <pr>(fr⟦icr⟧th"st⟦oomac⟧l`)</pr> }</mhw>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>fri⟦edh⟧st⟦omac⟧</ets>l. See <er>Fred</er>,
and <er>Stool</er>.]</ety> <def>A seat in churches near the altar, to
which offenders formerly fled for sanctuary.</def> <altsp>[Written
variously <asp>fridstool</asp>, <asp>freedstool</asp>, etc.]</altsp>
